    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a nice luster, though you will find some minor surface scratches and small stone chips on the front bumper from normal highway driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid, honest car without the premium price of a mint-condition showpiece.",
