    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute beauty! I've babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, regularly detailed, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like a dream and is in truly pristine condition inside and out. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make the next owner super happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
