      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in mechanical purity. This example features the high-revving S54 straight-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and precise VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Structural integrity is guaranteed with a proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing refreshed bushings to maintain its legendary handling characteristics. Meticulously maintained with documented valve adjustments and rod bearing replacement, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
