    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly immaculate, showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, swirls, or door dings to be found. The factory alloy wheels are flawless, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine materials; the leather remains supple and matte, free from any wear or creasing, and the original scent remains fresh. Every button, switch, and high-tech feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with an open-checkbook policy. It comes with a comprehensive service history, all original keys, and the factory manuals. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved specimen for the most discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
